{"tid":1893620,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"甜一刻改用芋圓控為芋圓供應商!!!","createTime":"2020-02-23T11:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T16:34:09.000Z","uid":61105,"like":505,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8057d9d19debacc523eabb02fbf6e844e5c732","tid":1893620,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"今朝碌下FB見到呢篇野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXGTzuH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXGTzuH.jpg&h=165438a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一直有人講左好耐，黃色經濟圈唔止係黃色餐廳圈/零售圈，最重要係建立完善既供應鍊（唔駛被人揸住春袋）同埋圈子既成員守望相助，尤其而家情況咁困難。<br />\n<br />\n成本雖然好大機會貴左，但我相信大部分人都唔會介意（如果係為左貪平我就唔會食黃店啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），希望黎緊有多d呢類合作出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想講兩間甜品舖都好高質，希望大家多多支持（芋圓控而家暫時以網店形式經營直至三月底）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：打手，兩間都食過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd784a6479e7fcfb8553c853fb41d531b81dd17","tid":1893620,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd93d9eab2b2abc02a11e5c67027ad90dff16cc1","tid":1893620,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d3f08e75a2a6f78a67fa965e8ec9ccb3db9db6","tid":1893620,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687e751a20f19f68ab639210ea75a2258916817a","tid":1893620,"uid":263213,