020-02-24T02:00:15.000Z","msg":"我去黃店係為咗幫到同路人同可以暢所欲言既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:01:42.000Z","msg":"不過記得發夢既野都唔好亂講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"當然 純粹一齊屌黑狗屌政府好正<br />\n有兩次印象特別深<br />\n一次係去重慶大廈食野個日 排左個幾鐘入去食咖哩 d人應該未試過一次過咁多人食 d單亂到仆街 但竟然無人屌 仲同隔離枱fd左一齊屌黑警<br />\n<br />\n第二次係前排未有肺炎個陣去左Tst Red Mr. 唱k. 好似唱完人話 跟住成班大嗌光復香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住無啦啦有人執枱既啱啱入黎執野 嗌左句時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉左佢坐低飲左杯先比佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe13da0657475a3a532a876b8396b204158a2030","tid":1893620,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedeaf4e4cdfd685c88913d046a8a0b5987e2f96","tid":1893620,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"515a6d794545a0d37d84c68d9cc36044115728b0","tid":1893620,"uid":25107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94fa670535aabf7402ce2dfa897815e093c0ddad","tid":1893620,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d071e3befd9b3838eff5e5e4e02939aae131c51","tid":1893620,"uid":25107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:00:15.000Z","msg":"我去黃店係為咗幫到同路人同可以暢所欲言既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:01:42.000Z","msg":"不過記得發夢既野都唔好亂講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"當然 純粹一齊屌黑狗屌政府好正<br />\n有兩次印象特別深<br />\n一次係去重慶大廈食野個日 排左個幾鐘入去食咖哩 d人應該未試過一次過咁多人食 d單亂到仆街 但竟然無人屌 仲同隔離枱fd左一齊屌黑警<br />\n<br />\n第二次係前排未有肺炎個陣去左Tst Red Mr. 唱k. 好似唱完人話 跟住成班大嗌光復香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住無啦啦有人執枱既啱啱入黎執野 嗌左句時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉左佢坐低飲左杯先比佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:13:55.000Z","msg":"我明呀，食都食得開心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3828622a7502b89210a5504fdc24e6b44436c6b9","tid":1893620,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06d6d0d13156b36fd119b2a5a5a0b137c0abc07","tid":1893620,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:51:17.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟一環扣一環 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec7ed2f09dcc449a88277db63b1c10fac3f84a9","tid":1893620,"uid":98909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:08:47.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"a9933f887fa1ac110cbf7d0e7fe2879250ee4861","tid":1893620,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa07156135f0f88cf56cce86cb09408afefed5a","tid":1893620,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c8057d9d19debacc523eabb02fbf6e844e5c732","tid":1893620,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"今朝碌下FB見到呢篇野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXGTzuH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXGTzuH.jpg&h=165438a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一直有人講左好耐，黃色經濟圈唔止係黃色餐廳圈/零售圈，最重要係建立完善既供應鍊（唔駛被人揸住春袋）同埋圈子既成員守望相助，尤其而家情況咁困難。<br />\n<br />\n成本雖然好大機會貴左，但我相信大部分人都唔會介意（如果係為左貪平我就唔會食黃店啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），希望黎緊有多d呢類合作出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想講兩間甜品舖都好高質，希望大家多多支持（芋圓控而家暫時以網店形式經營直至三月底）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：打手，兩間都食過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7dab25a21881a157f4b7e43f33ae592d9549fe63","tid":1893620,"uid":21965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"301e5515e3a1f9f9f7e6032c78e0c9c454c70e73","tid":1893620,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"甜一刻好食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日去買外賣，見佢仲有酒精搓手液賣，價錢隨意，重點係個樽畫左文宣，好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340e76f1be2ae15ebd4a69903edf99ab6db365cd","tid":1893620,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"呢個post啲人連甜一刻都話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食松記都好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9fa4ee9129fdced2cbc9619dec9be37ae6e213","tid":1893620,"uid":74554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:36:00.000Z","msg":"做多一步係好事"},{"pid":"c1c55a2b0fc2703bf9def2804239e46fd11ee3de","tid":1893620,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:36:32.000Z","msg":"屌，呢啲真係要狠狠地懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb98e386c7c47d730a218c17a63558701d950573","tid":1893620,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1c55a2b0fc2703bf9def2804239e46fd11ee3de","tid":1893620,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:36:32.000Z","msg":"屌，呢啲真係要狠狠地懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08: